What a way to start the new year! I got early copies of my book in the mail today and I am beyond ecstatic ✨ A project I’ve been working on for a while feels real now that I get to hold it in my hands! And it’s an even more surreal feeling to add it to my collection of @nobrowpress @flyingeyebooks books. Excited for you all to read it soon :)
.

Have you been wanting to preorder Juniper Mae but haven’t yet? Well, GOOD NEWS! @barnesandnoble is doing a 25% off ALL PREORDERS promotion on their website, which includes my book! Starting today until this Friday (01/25/23-01/27/23), use code “PREORDER25” at checkout! So any preorder books you’ve been eyeing, now is the time :) “Juniper Mae: Knight of Tykotech City” will be released March 7th, 2023 // #junipermae #junialbieadventures #knightoftykotech #barnesandnoble #nobrow #flyingeyebooks
Anyone chopped a lot of onions last night 🙃? #thelastofus

This was one of the first finished artworks I did of Juniper Mae a few years ago and it’s still one of my personal favorites. I used the image as my wallpaper to remind myself to keep going. I’ve carried her story with me for the last few years and I’m still in excited disbelief that I get to share it with you all next month ✨
.
Juniper Mae: Knight of Tykotech City comes out March 7th, preorder available through Amazon, B&N, Target, and Walmart #junipermae #junialbieadventures #knightoftykotechcity #nobrowpress #flyingeyebooks #procreate

✨ONE MORE MONTH✨ Another very early illustration I did of our good girl and boy. They’ve gone through very few changes since I’ve done this drawing but still the same at the heart of it. How time has flown and the book is coming out in one month on March 7th! Can’t wait for you all to meet Juniper Mae and Albie 👧🐸
.
#junipermae #junialbieadventures #knightoftykotechcity #nobrowpress #flyingeyebooks #procreate

✨River Island Kids x Flying Eye Books✨ this upcoming Sunday (Feb 12th, 3pm GMT / 7am PT / 10am ET), I’ll be doing an IG live session with @riverislandkids and @flyingeyebooks , drawing the two kiddos Juniper and Albie from my upcoming book while answering some questions from the most wonderful @niamhetc !
.
They will also be hosting a friendly comic competition (comic strip template will be available on the River Island website) and you’ll get the chance to win £250 River Island gift card, a bundle of Flying Eye books and your comic printed and framed!
.
Tune in and join us on Sunday if you can :) I look forward to it!
.
#riverislandkids #flyingeyebooks #nobrowpress #junipermae #junialbieadventures

LOOK AT THIS! FLIPPIN LOOK AT THIS AMAZINGNESS!! 😍 Can you hear me screaming?!! I’m obsessed and can’t get over this most wonderful awesome animation (and surprise) that @megsmcshane @mcyangin did of Juniper and Albie! I’m in absolute awe and just so grateful to know such two most wonderful people 💖 ! Thank you, thank you, thank you!
.
Megan and Matt make the most wonderful and wholesome animation in their spare time that you should most definitely check out! And they have a YouTube channel (in their profile) where they do live streams of their animations ✨
.
Just OBSESSED.
.
#mattandmegs #miteandmage #junipermae #junialbieadventures #knightoftykotechcity

✨HAPPY BOOK RELEASE DAY✨ Juniper Mae: Knight of Tykotech City is officially out in the US today and I’m so excited to share the first part of the story with you all! Hope that young readers will be able find the courage, strength and voice to be true warriors at heart ❤️ 

Thanks to the wonderful @niamhetc for your guiding support, @mancalledtim my partner in crime (get ready to see his name on the next book!), @lillygottwald designer extraordinaire, and @nobrowpress @flyingeyebooks for making a lifelong dream come true!

Juniper Mae: Knight of Tykotech City is available through Amazon, Barnes & Noble, Target, and Walmart

Oh HEY! I’m so excited to share that more Juniper and Albie adventures continue with the next book in the series ✨Juniper Mae: Secrets of the Guardian Knights✨
 
Join our little heroes as they continue their adventures deep in the forest! With new discoveries and inventions, it leads them to a whole new journey that not only threatens their lives, but also the forest!
 
Done with writing partner-in-crime, Tim Fraser (@mancalledtim ), we’re so excited to share our little heroes next story with you all! Also shout-out to dream team @niamhetc @lillygottwald to being the most supportive ladies ❤️ And another shout-out to @flyingeyebooks for making the dream come true.
 
Juniper Mae: The Secret of the Guardian Knights will be coming out April 2024 in the US and UK. Pre-orders available through Amazon, Barnes & Noble, Target, Walmart, Waterstones, and your local indie bookshop!
